companyInfo.introduction: Cng ty C phn CIC39 (C32) ctin thn l Cng ty Kinh doanh Pht trin nh Sng B, thnh lp vo nm 1993.C32 chuyn sang hot ng theo m hnh cng ty c phn t nm 2008. Cng ty hot ng chnh trong lnh vc lnh vc xy lp, cng b tng, bt ng sn, kinh doanh vt liu xy dng.Th trng hot ng chnh ca cng ty bao gm cc tnh Bnh Dng, thnh ph H Ch Minh, ng Nai v Ty Ninh. Nm 2011, cng ty m rng xy dng nh xng sn xut cng B tng ti x Long Nguyn, huyn Bn Ct tnh Bnh Dng vi cng sut 30.000 cng/ nm, ng thi a vo hot ng dy chuyn sn xut gch b tng t chn, gch block... a sn phm mi vo th trng.
companyInfo.notes:
- Ngy 08/01/1993: Tin thn l Cng ty Kinh doanh Pht trin nh Sng B (SB.P.Corp), l doanh nghip Nh nc c thnh lp theo quyt nh s 06/Q-UB ca UBND tnh Sng B.

- Nm 1997: Cng ty i tn thnh Cng ty u t Xy dng 3/2.

- Ngy 11/12/2008: Cng ty u t Xy dng 3/2 chnh thc chuyn i sang m hnh CTCP vi tn gi CTCP u t Xy dng 3-2 vi vn iu l l 112 t ng.

- Nm 2010: Giao dch trn th trng UPCOM.

- Nm 2012: Nim yt trn S Giao dch Chng khon Thnh ph H Ch Minh (HOSE).

- Ngy 03/08/2017: Tng vn iu l ln 136.64 t ng.

- Ngy 08/08/2018: Tng vn iu l ln 150.3 t ng.

- Ngy 18/05/2020: i tn thnh CTCP CIC39.
